{"tid":1706762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上熱門] 每次行動唔好做既一件事","createTime":"2019-11-11T07:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T07:13:16.000Z","uid":273740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9154f2c2905f50e2ca61af9ca8445c44ca175d50","tid":1706762,"uid":273740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:09:12.000Z","msg":"CCTVB 每日都塗毒港人<br />\n好似今朝開槍事件，佢完全冇播過事前示威者根本手無寸鐵既片。旁白就講話警察為左制服示威者，因此開槍。上左年紀既人就咁睇以為示威者對D 狗有威脅，所以開槍合理化<br />\n而類似既新聞每日都播緊，洗緊大家腦，塗毒緊港人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家之後每次活動千奇唔好搵CCTVB 既人出黎，人地無片出街好陰公。"},{"pid":"0fcae4670af8272fc9fb9b472a44be43f23f332c","tid":1706762,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得欣賞下個剪接<br />\n聽下笑話<br />\n係可以睇下既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/NL1Ttj0DnrM/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FNL1Ttj0DnrM%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=6fbb33ee&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}